test_name: FRMDATEB4L earliest date allowed
short_desc: FRMDATEB4L must not be from date before form was released
full_desc: Q0a. FRMDATEB4L (B4L form date) must not be from date before form was released (2017)
test_logic: IF FRMDATEB4L before (01/01/2017)

test_name: LBDELDST compared to LBDELFRQ and LBDELSEV
short_desc: If (LBDELFRQ = 4 or LBDELSEV = 3), then LBDELDST should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q1j. LBDELFRQ (Frequency of delusions) = 4 (Very frequent - once or more per day) or Q1k. LBDELSEV (Severity of delusions) = 3 (Majorly disruptive), then Q1l. LBDELDST (How emotionally distressing do you find this behavior?) should not equal 0 (Not at all)
test_logic: IF (LBDELFRQ = 4 or LBDELSEV = 3) and LBDELDST = 0

test_name: LBHALDST compared to LBHALFRQ and LBHALSEV
short_desc: If (LBHALFRQ = 4 or LBHALSEV = 3), LBHALDST should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q2h. LBHALFRQ (Frequency of hallucinations) = 4 (Very frequent - once or more per day) or Q2i. LBHALSEV (Severity of hallucinations) = 3 (Majorly disruptive), then Q2j. LBHALDST (How emotionally distressing do you find this behavior?) should not equal 0 (Not at all)
test_logic: IF (LBHALFRQ = 4 or LBHALSEV = 3) and LBHALDST = 0

test_name: LBANXDST compared to LBANXFRQ and LBANXSEV
short_desc: If (LBANXFRQ = 4 or LBANXSEV = 3), LBANXDST should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q3h. LBANXFRQ (Frequency of anxiety) = 4 (Very frequent - once or more per day) or Q3i. LBANXSEV (Severity of anxiety) = 3 (Majorly distressing, then Q3j. LBANXDST (How emotionally distressing do you find this behavior?) should not equal 0 (Not at all)
test_logic: IF (LBANXFRQ = 4 or LBANXSEV = 3) and LBANXDST = 0

test_name: LBAPADST compared to LBAPAFRQ and LBAPASEV
short_desc: If (LBAPAFRQ = 4 or LBAPASEV = 3), LBAPADST should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q4i. LBAPAFRQ (Frequency of apathy) = 4 (Very frequent - once or more per day) or Q4j. LBAPASEV (Severity of apathy) = 3 (Majorly evident), then Q4k. LBAPADST (How emotionally distressing do you find this behavior?) should not equal 0 (Not at all)
test_logic: IF (LBAPAFRQ = 4 or LBAPASEV = 3) and LBAPADST = 0

test_name: LBDELAGE compared to LBDELUS
short_desc: If (LBDELUS is in (0,8) and (LBHALL=1 or LBANXIET=1 or LBAPATHY=1)), then LBDELAGE must equal 888
full_desc: If (Q1.LBDELUS (Delusions) is in (0,8) (No or Not applicable), and (Q2. LBHALL (Hallucinations)=1 or Q3. LBANXIET (Anxiety)=1 or Q4. LBAPATHY (Apathy)=1)), then Q6a. LBDELAGE (Age of onset of delusions) must equal 888 (Not applicable)
test_logic: If (LBDELUS is in (0,8) and (LBHALL=1 or LBANXIET=1 or LBAPATHY=1)) and LBDELAGE ne 888

test_name: LBHALAGE compared to LBHALL
short_desc: If (LBHALL is in (0,8) and (LBDELUS=1 or LBANXIET=1 or LBAPATHY=1)), then LBHALAGE must equal 888

test_logic: If (LBHALL is in (0,8) and (LBDELUS=1 or LBANXIET=1 or LBAPATHY=1)) and LBHALAGE ne 888

test_name: LBANXAGE compared to LBANXIET

full_desc: If (Q3. LBANXIET (Anxiety) is in (0,8) (No or Not applicable), and (Q1. LBDELUS (Delusions)=1 or Q2. LBHALL (Hallucinations)=1 or Q4. LBAPATHY (Apathy)=1)), then Q8a. LBHALAGE (Age of onset of anxiety) must equal 888 (Not applicable)

full_desc: If (Q4. LBAPATHY (Apathy) is in (0,8) (No or Not applicable), and (Q1. LBDELUS (Delusions)=1 or Q2. LBHALL (Hallucinations)=1 or Q3. LBANXIET (Anxiety)=1)), then Q9a. LBAPAAGE (Age of onset of Apathy) must equal 888 (Not applicable)
test_logic: If (LBAPATHY is in (0,8) and (LBDELUS=1 or LBHALL=1 or LBANXIET=1)) and LBAPAAGE ne 888

test_name: LBDELUS compared to UDS Form B5 DEL
